realtime strategy of risk. 

Simple rock paper scissor formate, infantry, tank, and artillary.

built off Unity.

Build units from city-cities can be captured be defeating city hp .

Cities grouped together will form a nation ie 7 cities scattered around france when united boost income and unlock flag.

Burnable terrain idea-trees can form forests as choke point but can be indvidually targetted down to create paths aside
from mountain chokepoints(mountains should be indistructable).

Simple 3 unit format should allow custom import of models ie switch from napoleon to modern day with simple package.
